Maruti Suzuki Says Labor Issue at Manesar Resolved, Workers Sign Agreement

-- B y   S i d d h a r t h   P h i l i p
-- 
2011-10-01T07:26:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-01/maruti-suzuki-says-labor-issue-at-manesar-resolved-workers-sign-agreement.html
Maruti Suzuki India Ltd. (MSIL)  said a labor
issue at its plant in Manesar had been resolved and an agreement
was signed with workers.  The striking employees will resume work on Oct. 3, the
company said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Siddharth Philip in Mumbai at 
